    <span style="font-size: 20px;">&nbsp;Welcome to <strong style="color:#2980b9;font-size: 24px;"> Kristu Jayanti College (MCA)</strong></span></h4>

<p style="text-align:justify;padding-top:15px;"> Kristu Jayanti College offers Master’s Degree in Computer Application (MCA) with the intention to produce competitive computer professionals in tune with advanced technical concepts. Our MCA course is a three year full time programme spanning six semesters, affiliated to the Bangalore University and approved by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE). The college puts the students through comprehensive and intensive training. This postgraduate course focuses on the subjects at an application level and includes topics like Advanced Database Management Systems, Operating Systems, Software Engineering, Artificial intelligence, Software Testing, Data Mining, Data Analytics and various open source software’s. The focused training given on these topics helps students to adapt themselves to the art and science of software development. Students work in an integrated environment that enables them to access the resources effectively for their academic purpose.</p>